'''''La maschera e il volto''''' is a comedy of [[grotesque]] genre by [[Luigi Chiarelli]]. Written in 1913 and first presented in 1916, it is [[History of ideas|historically significant]] for starting the contemporary grotesque theatre.<ref>[http://www.atuttascuola.it/collaborazione/angelotti/luigi_chiarelli.htm Luigi Chiarelli - La maschera e il volto] su atuttascuola.it</ref> It had a great success first in Italy and then internationally, and continues to be represented. Several movies have been adapted from the play.

