Manjhan '''''Madhumalati''''' is an [[India|Indian]] [[Sufi]] text, written in 1545 by Mir Sayyid Manjhan Shattari Rajgiri.<ref>{{cite book|last1=Behl|first1=Aditya|title=Love's Subtle Magic: An Indian Islamic Literary Tradition, 1379-1545|date=2012|publisher=OUP USA|isbn=9780195146707|page=23|url=https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=PK7riKO6IN8C&pg=PR7&dq=Madhumalati+sufi&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwj5n6ft7__XAhXsJ8AKHWxXBSkQ6AEILjAB#v=onepage&q=Madhumalati%20sufi&f=false|accessdate=10 December 2017|language=en}}</ref>  

